<plot>In this musical comedy a young women laments about her facial blemishes and questions what true beauty really is. Through unique storytelling, it is revealed how her family, friends and co-workers try to mold her into their ideals (despite her resistance) and fail . The women finds true love, acceptance and beauty when she learns to believe in the power of herself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?619574</url></doc>
